Connect pairs of matching Halloween characters by creating a path between them.
Click / Tap and drag to connect the Halloween. Play now!

Collect more than 5 gifts to get a spell (power-up) which will show up on the right side of the screen.  Cast spells by dragging and dropping it on the target. Description:
Reach 100 is a game about puzzle and reflexion in which you must regroup numbers  to create sums of 100.  You have the possibility to slide the different forms and numbers, horizontally and vertically, and add numbers to each other.  If you reach the sum of 100, this form freezes and cannot be used anymore.  Regroup all forms to reach the end of the level.
Put your neurons to the trial and find the solutions on sixty different levels. Levels are becoming more and more complexes.

-	60 levels
-	180 stars to collect
-	Thinking game
-	Addictive gameplay

Title: Easter Pic Slider
Description: "Easter Pic Slider" is a delightful puzzle game that brings the Easter spirit to your device. Your task is to rearrange the pieces of Easter images by moving them between tiles, arranging them in ascending order. Tap or click a block to shift it to an adjacent blank space. Be mindful of the ticking clock; you'll lose points with each passing second. So, strategize wisely to complete the puzzle and maximize your score. Get ready for a challenging and festive Easter experience!
Instructions: Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.

For this, you have to choose one of the surrounding tiles’ color from bottom of the screen. There are 6 colors in total and your final goal is to make all tiles have the same color in 22 moves or less.
Instructions: Touch on mobile device or mouse on PC.

Title: Fisherman Sliding Puzzles
Description: Fisherman Sliding Puzzles is an engaging sliding jigsaw puzzle game. Your task is to move pieces of images to recreate the picture displayed on the right side of the screen. With 8 exciting and challenging levels, test your puzzle-solving skills and piece together each scene!
Instructions: Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.

Title: Around the World in 2 Seconds

The only thing that can stop you is Eifel Tower, because it's very long and it's hard to jump over it! Try to travel around the world as many times as you can and score higher!
Instructions: Touch on mobile device or mouse on PC

Title: The Mole Knocker

PLAYER 1: "W,A,S,D" or "MOUSE"
PLAYER 2: "ARROW KEYS"

Title: My Totoro Room
Description: Design a super-cute bedroom devoted to Totoro, the adorable anime classic.
Instructions: Use your mouse to select all decorations to make your ideal Totoro Room.

Title: Equal Alphabets
Description: "Equal Alphabets" is a delightful game that combines picture recognition and alphabet practice. Your task is to match pictures that feature objects starting with the same letter. Simply click or touch an image and drag it to its matching counterpart. To earn a bonus, complete each level within 2 minutes. You'll score 500 points for correct matches but face a 100-point penalty for incorrect ones. Your mission is to conquer all 12 levels and emerge as the ultimate alphabet master!
Instructions: Use mouse or touch to play this game.

Title: Find the Odd 2
Description: "Find the Odd 2" is a vibrant and engaging puzzle game that challenges you to identify the one different item from a group of four. Pay close attention to the hint displayed on the screen and find the unique item within 25 seconds to earn a time bonus. Conquer all 30 exciting levels and sharpen your observational skills in this colorful puzzle adventure. Can you triumph in this challenge? Give it a try and find out!
Instructions: Use mouse to touch the items.

Title: 4x4 Halloween

The blocks will cross over the iron bridges automatically. You have to plan your moves and use the right order. Twisted Rods is a game that has 3D graphics and engine. It is a fun and soothing game that tests your logic and vision. How many levels can you complete? Play now and find out!

Title: Classic Puzzle Game

Title: Dungeon Box

The ball moves in the dungeon and when it comes to the bottom, you have to summon the wall and block it so it stays within the room.

If you collect only 1 item in a turn, 200 points will be deducted from your score.

Note that it is not an easy game and it even becomes more difficult as you progress because these squares will move faster and faster!

Title: Rectangular Path

But if you don’t want to hit the walls or the square itself, then you have to turn at the right time or otherwise you will lose! So just tap the screen at the right time and around the corners to turn and continue your path!

After each time that you change the ball’s color, it will also change the direction that it moves. You will lose if you fail to change the ball’s color correctly or if you change it when it’s not necessary.

Touch on mobile device(touch left side of screen for single jump and touch on right side for double jump).

Enter the captivating world of Energy Clicker and become a true master of electricity generation! However, be careful because if the energy exceeds the permissible value, your generator will start to break down!
